author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Metal Gear Solid Delta. While I love MGS3, this re-release of the game is frankly a bit insulting in regards to the performance for a full priced release and deserves to be called out. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Please Stop Defending Konami...
